        <abstract>
            <p>Corrects his former account of cowslips.</p>
            <p>The delay in the publication of JS’s Primula paper.</p>
            <p>Delights in JS’s experimentation on Verbascum which confirms [C. F.] Gärtner’s statements.</p>
            <p>Should be pleased if JS would accept offer of help.</p>
